<div class="container mx-auto px-3 py-5 space-y-4 md:px-16">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <h2 data-scroll class="text-4xl text-center nunito font-bold">About Us</h2>
    <article class="space-y-8">
      <p class="text-justify">
        Welcome to Surbhi Metal and Alloys - A perfect solution for all your metal
        requirements. Surbhi Metal and Alloys having it's registered office in
        Mumbai. Surbhi Metal and Alloys is a team of experienced industry experts
        who deal in manufacturing, supplying and trading of ferrous and non
        ferrous metals.
        <br />
        <br />
        We manufacture and supply a variety of ferrous and non ferrous metals such
